{"tid":324950,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"自己換engine oil有咩注意？","createTime":"2017-07-17T00:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T10:16:42.000Z","uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01c7acde8eda5b02f4716774a1be6d7986f2f7d8","tid":324950,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:15:57.000Z","msg":"一直都係叫人搞，今次想試下自己換。<br />\n想問下新油就咁倒入去有咩後果？<br />\nengine oil 點分邊隻好唔好？"},{"pid":"b21701123c43d5d3cb352907c04520f51e860d7f","tid":324950,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直都係叫人搞，今次想試下自己換。<br />\n想問下新油就咁倒入去有咩後果？<br />\nengine oil 點分邊隻好唔好？</blockquote><br />\n唔識搞都係比人搞啦<br />\n你有無啲器具啊"},{"pid":"26495272bd161b904f72971bfda676d7427330b7","tid":324950,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直都係叫人搞，今次想試下自己換。<br />\n想問下新油就咁倒入去有咩後果？<br />\nengine oil 點分邊隻好唔好？</blockquote><br />\n要放舊油同換過濾先倒新油<br />\n你就咁倒會港瀉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23232952618cb6f073ba0aa5b754a381a06e37bb","tid":324950,"uid":90739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"想問ching打算點升起架車？"},{"pid":"70023f49d0731eeadb15e985f1c86320cdf426b2","tid":324950,"uid":98262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:24:52.000Z","msg":"扭鬆左油隔先放油<br />\n如果你放哂油先發現個油隔扭唔鬆既話就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f1df5a6d4cd4c22b0198cfbc263864635206b2","tid":324950,"uid":19715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n兩條木方都得啦"},{"pid":"fdbe7d7fc10f92f99bdb462080215aa0484fb187","tid":324950,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n佢叫我幫佢單手拎起架車, 再&quot;登&quot;幾下, &quot;登&quot;哂D油出黎先"},{"pid":"b29200bc8ce8533e43ad7be28cb0707bf721dac9","tid":324950,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n唧起之後用凳仔托住"},{"pid":"ae63e6c5b43226d17100101070c404f67e0a81d5","tid":324950,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05a12191cf81df0b305fbdc347e5297609cbadf8","tid":324950,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4943ac3a23ce151489d997b0b858110420305f41","tid":324950,"uid":9766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n唧起之後用凳仔托住</blockquote><br />\n凳仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/135001_babf3e57c9912e933a6c374230b7fa74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F135001_babf3e57c9912e933a6c374230b7fa74.jpg&h=d7422e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個唔夠黎兩個🖖🏿<br />\n<br />\n不過講番，你啲廢油如果倒落渠係犯法，你最好搵個容器黎比番啲廢油處理既車房。"},{"pid":"30026149d2aaf67edeed3f09fe1af00c2f0f0b6a","tid":324950,"uid":100474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"扭個filter入去扭太鬆會漏 太緊會會爛中間一塊鐵圈"},{"pid":"efd76abbf5eb0b50ea8a766d66494db66a5ca4a6","tid":324950,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b9c32b258e1cdad4488339511a25250994cf211","tid":324950,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直都係叫人搞，今次想試下自己換。<br />\n想問下新油就咁倒入去有咩後果？<br />\nengine oil 點分邊隻好唔好？</blockquote><br />\n要平就去孖八去換，人工都加多150-200"},{"pid":"c790d8a738fff298af53c144ea056fb80b4d9b8c","tid":324950,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你拎油出去車房人工都係150-200，有d仲要唔係唧起，係升起成架車，<br />\n放油真係放得晒，唔同深水步某間唧起半邊車，放唔晒油又快手快腳。<br />\n整到成手都係，200蚊咪比人賺</blockquote><br />\n邊間成間唧起好介紹, 重好多油款比我簡下<br />\n<br />\n我都想轉會, 唔去深水埗個間"},{"pid":"fedf26a07c18b0affbae463b60f9b6b18c57d965","tid":324950,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n唧起之後用凳仔托住</blockquote><br />\n凳仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n知唔知咩叫凳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec500c2d8c9a3fb4c62608e8ad29e45131182539","tid":324950,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問ching打算點升起架車？</blockquote><br />\n唧起之後用凳仔托住</blockquote><br />\n凳仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/135001_babf3e57c9912e933a6c374230b7fa74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F135001_babf3e57c9912e933a6c374230b7fa74.jpg&h=d7422e53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個唔夠黎兩個🖖🏿<br />\n<br />\n不過講番，你啲廢油如果倒落渠係犯法，你最好搵個容器黎比番啲廢油處理既車房。</blockquote><br />\n夠力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/165355_6eee91ec065ba273d008f2853a0991a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F165355_6eee91ec065ba273d008f2853a0991a4.jpg&h=77118c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3 tones 都夠頂"},{"pid":"afd017021dacfdf589179180a764e3a4c64ae0d7","tid":324950,"uid":12523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你拎油出去車房人工都係150-200，有d仲要唔係唧起，係升起成架車，<br />\n放油真係放得晒，唔同深水步某間唧起半邊車，放唔晒油又快手快腳。<br />\n整到成手都係，200蚊咪比人賺</blockquote><br />\n邊間成間唧起好介紹, 重好多油款比我簡下<br />\n<br />\n我都想轉會, 唔去深水埗個間</blockquote><br />\nOn9先會去孖8"},{"pid":"a4078bc93506ba5a470a761ab9169488ab1aa28e","tid":324950,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8fd433e5266bab8b2f36ead8c18da1f74a0399e","tid":324950,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6506016085c1aa66653e647b74106f014c7f98c3","tid":324950,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你拎油出去車房人工都係150-200，有d仲要唔係唧起，係升起成架車，<br />\n放油真係放得晒，唔同深水步某間唧起半邊車，放唔晒油又快手快腳。<br />\n整到成手都係，200蚊咪比人賺</blockquote><br />\n邊間成間唧起好介紹, 重好多油款比我簡下<br />\n<br />\n我都想轉會, 唔去深水埗個間</blockquote><br />\nOn9先會去孖8</blockquote><br />\n住係隔離街, 次次夠期換都收工等到8-9點先去88換, 又唔洗排又唔係貴<br />\n<br />\n個頭重有冇好介紹"},{"pid":"460cb99b5790bb76fd3d9ab1a2b1755294c55444","tid":324950,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"我之前都係自己換<br />\n架生有飛機"},{"pid":"57f597d8c569845583ae9d824ef67a071c0a3e8e","tid":324950,"uid":59030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T09:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都係自己換<br />\n架生有飛機</blockquote><br />\n即x2 登仔x2 磅尺一枝 油隔匙/砂紙  漏斗"},{"pid":"5130a214844cb24a5fdcbe966ec485d1eb8bd8fa","tid":324950,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"去油站換吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436575a1c278ab76a0d1460d912ed7b2c5f4b19b","tid":324950,"uid":68516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去油站換吧喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa